name: **Inishbollog**
description: Inishbollog L936-914 Sheet 31 Small island, unkempt in 2012, but someone loves it. Ungrazed and going to seed, there is a stairway from the sandy landing at the E tip to the summit plateau, and even plantings of New Zealand flax and some struggling alders.. Must have been grazed until recently and hopefully will be again.
